			<div class="comment-body"><p>Thanks for posting Jeff. The point I was trying to make was that you can&#8217;t map any keys in Avid to Alt+ __ or Cmd + __  Its the keys as they are, or shift and the keys as the only modifier. In FCP (as an example) you have 11 modifier options. The keys, cmd, alt, ctrl, shift, shift-cmd, shift-alt, cmd-alt, cmd-ctrl, ctrl-shift, ctrl-alt. Avid just seems a little restrictive in comparison!</p>
</div>

